---
title: Orange Sesame Chicken & Jasmine Rice with Cucumber Salad
description: Did someone say orange chicken? These sticky, sweet and sesame-coated pieces of golden juicy chicken are bringing back memories of takeaway meals from our childhood. And on the table in fifteen minutes? We don’t think it gets much better than that!

